*.rsuser
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Visual Studio cache and temporary files
.vs/
.vscode/
*.cache
*.temp
*.tmp
*.log

## Database and Entity Framework
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.sdf
Migrations/

## Environment secrets (MUITO IMPORTANTE)
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.pem

## Kubernetes / Docker related
.docker/
*.kubeconfig
*.kube/

## Operating System files
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
